abstract: A march north from Zuccotti Park under the watchful eye of the police.
snippet: A march north from Zuccotti Park under the watchful eye of the police.
lead_paragraph: 11:03 p.m. | Updated More than 1,000 Occupy Wall Street demonstrators streamed across the threshold of Washington Square Park on Saturday afternoon after a spirited but conflict-free march from the financial district.

headline.main: Wall Street Protest Visits Washington Sq.
